TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content: Waiter, there's a lander in my soup.

No.

Waiter, Catbert ate my soup.

THE SUN IS A DEADLY LAZER

 

Waiter, there's a weird meme in my soup!

Well, the soup is anti-memetic.

 

 

Waiter ! I think you left something on my soup...

Edited March 13, 2018 by YNM

What?

Wqaiter, there's a @WinkAllKerb'' in my soup!

Umm, you weren't supposed to see that. Security!

Waiter, there's a bunch of paperclips in my soup.

Yes, the soup of the day is "Clippy" soup, sir

Waiter! There's a Wookie in my soup!

Yes, the soup of the day is "Harry" soup, named after Mr. Harry, our founder.

 

Waiter, there's a KS-25x4 "Mammoth" in my soup!

Sir, upon closer inspection, it's simply a bowl of 100 moths; exaggerating a bit, aren't we?

Waitress! I ordered a bowl of peanut butter broth, and you delivered a simple peanut swimming in lukewarm water!

Sorry. We are still trying to catch a butterfly to add it to other flies in the broth.

Waiter! A toasted breadfly, please!

The breadfly toaster is already on the cashier sir, I'll lead the way.

 

 

 

Waiter ? Did my soup survives ?

No, your soup didn't make it. We're sorry for your loss, and the soup's funeral will be on the 24th.

Waiter, my soup is hovering a few inches off the table and glowing.

Please, get out from the kitchen. Out radiation oven is dangerous for everyone without a cook's lead apron.

Waiter! Potassium iodide, please.

I’m sorry, that’s not on the menu anymore. You missed it by 1.14 seconds.

 

Waiter, there are chicken and noodles in my soup!

Yes, I know, you wanted a vegan noodle soup.
But the chicken tried to pick the noodles and fell down.
Btw do you prefer the feathers removed?

Waiter! A cup of TEA, please! And a glass of TEB.
